{"tid":2229092,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"中國佛山日本街 動畫招牌消失：據說為因為日本關注侵權問題","createTime":"2020-10-04T06:31:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-04T12:25:42.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"15b7853316a709f8ae34c570a3fa150eb2c0000a","tid":2229092,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T06:31:34.000Z","msg":"【#LikeJapan生活】中國佛山日本街 動畫招牌消失：據說為因為日本關注侵權問題<br />\n<br />\n近日在網上流傳一個影片，內容是之前受到多方關注，位於中國佛山的日本街，當地多個動畫招牌消失，更一度有傳是愛國人士清走。據說真正原因，是因為日本關注當地侵權問題，所以他們才會換走版權圖片。<br />\n<br />\n例如圖中所拍到的《ONE PIECE》招牌，對比富士新聞網9月28日的報導的情況，現時招牌已沒有了作品LOGO與作者尾田榮一郎的字眼。<br />\n<br />\n日本媒體 關注中國「日本街」：<a href=\"http://www.likejapan.com/s/fatshanjpstreet\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.likejapan.com%2Fs%2Ffatshanjpstreet&d=eUEb8trTAlhqW9E3j8wil3r2%2BPVmRcyv9paqmPGdWjc%3D&h=851d93b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.likejapan.com/s/fatshanjpstreet</a><br />\n<br />\nby #Likejapan_Owen<br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝<br />\n【日本開運魚食譜】升「漬」油甘魚片為你帶來「出人頭地」！&darr;<br />\n<a href=\"https://rebrand.ly/JFOODOBT\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Frebrand.ly%2FJFOODOBT&d=eUEb8trTAlhqW9E3j8wil3r2%2BPVmRcyv9paqmPGdWjc%3D&h=f96f4320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://rebrand.ly/JFOODOBT</a><br />\n<br />\nLikeJapan YouTube每星期更新節目！請多多支持：<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/channel/UCZviX79dSpGwN5cLOl2FPPg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCZviX79dSpGwN5cLOl2FPPg&d=eUEb8trTAlhqW9E3j8wil3r2%2BPVmRcyv9paqmPGdWjc%3D&h=abc40c85\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.youtube.com/channel/UCZviX79dSpGwN5cLOl2FPPg</a>"},{"pid":"dc3fadc10a9087bbd0f4412ccfc25f2ea84fa18c","tid":2229092,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T06:32:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dc8iYdC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdc8iYdC.jpg&h=a9d65219&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />